></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Horace Vernet, La prise de Malakoff, 1858, Mus&eacute;e Rolin, Autun &nbsp;47:52(2), 48:38(2)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Le Gray, Le Pav&eacute; de Chailly, 1856-1857, tirage sur papier sal&eacute; d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s n&eacute;gatif sur verre, 23,9x33cm, The Museum of Fine Arts, Houston, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp;1:34(3), 2:10(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Rosa Bonheur, For&ecirc;t de Fontainebleau: Printemps dans les bois, 1860-1865, huile sur toile, non document&eacute; &nbsp;2:24(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Benjamin Brecknell Turner, Hedgerow Trees at Clerkenleap, Worcestershire, c.1850, &nbsp;tirage sur papier albumin&eacute; sur n&eacute;gatif calotype, Victoria and Albert Museum, Londres, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;2:37(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-t