u (For&ecirc;t de Fontainebleau), c.1833, huile sur papier, verg&eacute; sur bois, 39,7x49,5cm, Metropolitain Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp;4:39(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Baptiste Camille Corot, The Leaning Tree Trunk (Tronc d&acute;arbre couch&eacute;), 1860-1865, huile sur toile, 49,7x60,7cm, The National Gallery of Art, Londres, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;4:50(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Adalbert Cuvelier, Environs d&acute;Arras, 1852&nbsp; 5:00(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Baptiste Camille Corot, Bord d&rsquo;un lac ou Souvenir d&acute;Italie, 1855-1860, huile sur toile, 22,9x31,8cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp;5:23(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">William Henry Fox Talbot, An Oak tree in Winter, c.1843, calotype n&eacute;gatif et tirage sur papier sal&eacute;, &nbsp;The British Library, Londres, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;5:33(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Baptiste Camille Corot, Canteleu pr&egrave;s de Rouen, c. 1872, huile sur toile, Mus&eacute;e des Beaux-Arts de la Ville de Paris, Petit Palais, Paris &nbsp; 5:42(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Le Gray, Tree Study, Forest of Fontainebleau (&Eacute;tude d&acute;arbre), c.1856, tirage &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s n&eacute;gatif sur verre, 31,8x41,4cm, Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, Etats-Unis &nbsp;6:05(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Charles-Fran&ccedil;ois Daubigny, Les Bords de l\'Oise, 1859, huile sur toile, 90x182cm, Mus&eacute;e des Beaux-Arts de Bordeaux, Bordeaux &nbsp;6:20(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Nadar, &laquo; Effet produit sur un visiteur du Salon par l\'eau des merveilleux tableaux de M. Daubigny. &raquo; Nadar Jury, dans Le Journal amusant, n&ordm;185, 16 juillet 1859&nbsp; 6:26(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=