h-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, Pizarro Seizing the Inca of Peru, 1846, huile sur toile, 12,8x17,1cm, Victoria and Albert Museum, Londres, Royaume-Uni &nbsp; 20:52(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, Chill October, 1870, huile sur toile, 141,1&times;186,7cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp;21:16(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, Murthly Moss, 1887, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp;21:32(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, The Sound of Many Waters, 1876, The National Trust for Scotland, Fyvie Castle, &Eacute;cosse</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Peter Henry Emerson, Gunner Working Up To Fowl, c1885, tirage argentique, dans Life and Landscape on the Norfolk Broads, c.1886, Ed. Valentine and Sons, George Eastman Museum, Rochester, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 21:50(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Peter Henry Emerson, A Rushy Shore, 1886, tirage argentique, 18,3x29,1cm, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Le Gray, La grande Vague, S&egrave;te, 1857, tirage argentique &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s n&eacute;gatif sur verre, n&ordm;17, 33,7x41,4cm, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, Etats-Unis &nbsp;22:39(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Le Gray, Marine, &eacute;tude de nuages, 1856-1857, &eacute;preuve sur papier albumin&eacute; &agrave; partir de deux n&eacute;gatifs verre au collodion, 32x39cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; 23:29(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Le Gray, Brick au clair de lune, 1856-1857, tirage &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine, 810cmx1030cm, The Nelson-Atkins Museum of Art &nbsp;23:57(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Oscar Gustave Rejlander, Hard Times, c.1860, &eacute;preuve sur papier albumin&eacute; d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s negatif sur verre, 13,9x19,9cm, Georges Eastman Museum, Rochester, Etats-Unis &nbsp;24:29(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Oscar Gustave Rejlander, Two ways of life, 1857, tirage au charbon, 40,6x76,2cm, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis 24:46(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henry Peach Robinson, When the Day\'s Work is Done, 1877, tirage &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s six n&eacute;gatifs s&eacute;par&eacute;s sur verre en collodion humide , Victoria and Albert Museum, Londres, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;26:04(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henry Peach Robinson, Fading Away (L&rsquo;Agonie), 1858, &eacute;preuve argentique sur papier albumin&eacute; &agrave; partir d\'un n&eacute;gatif sur verre, 23,8x37,2cm, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp;27:04(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Henry Peach Robinson, Bringing home the May, 1862, 40x23cm, Royal Photographic Society - Science &amp; Society Picture Library &nbsp;27:55(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, Portrait of John Ruskin, 1853-1854, huile sur toile, 71,3x60,8cm, Ashmolean Museum, Oxford, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;28:15(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, Automn Leaves, 1856, huile sur toile, 104x73,6cm, City Art Galleries, Manchester, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;28:42(3), 29:35(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, Apple Blossoms ou Spring, 1858-1859, huile sur toile, 113x179,3cm, Lady Lever Art Gallery, Liverpool, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;29:48(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">John Everett Millais, The Woodsman\'s Daughter (La Fille du b&ucirc;cheron), 1850-1851, huile sur toile, 88,9x64,7cm, Guildhall Art Gallery, Londres, Royaume-Uni &nbsp;30:10(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Arthur Hughes, Home from Sea (Retour de mer), 1862, huile sur panneau, 50&times;65cm, Ashmolean Museum, Oxford, Royaume-Uni&nbsp; &nbsp;31:14(3)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `videosonline` (`id`, `title_fr`, `subtitle_fr`, `text_fr`, `texto_secondary_fr`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `image`, `color`, `home_image`, `title`, `subtitle`, `text`, `texto_secondary`, `bio`, `ilustraciones`, `order`) VALUES
(17, 'Photographie et Peinture, II', 'Quand la photographie n\'était pas encore un art...', '<p class=\"font_8\">Une histoire de la peinture ne serait compl&egrave;te sans une &eacute;tude approfondie de la relation qu\'elle entretint avec la photographie. &Agrave; cette &eacute;poque, l\'une et l\'autre se toisent et se conjuguent le plus discr&egrave;tement possible.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">Les r&eacute;volutions artistiques qui se multipli&egrave;rent au XIXe, faisant se succ&eacute;der R&eacute;alisme, Impressionnisme et Post impressionnisme sont &eacute;troitement li&eacute;es au d&eacute;veloppement de la photographie, car cette derni&egrave;re d&eacute;clencha une crise identitaire de la peinture qui, de fait, perdit en quelques d&eacute;cades son exclusivit&eacute; &agrave; rendre le visuel... Et la peinture fut contrainte &agrave; se d&eacute;passer.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">Cette conf&eacute;rence permettra de visualiser l\'impact discret de la photographie sur la peinture entre 1855 et 1885.</p>', 'Au contact du cliché photographique, les réalistes développent des talents d’hyper-réalistes, les peintres d’avant-garde nourrissent leur originalité.', '2024-10-12 02:23:00', '2024-10-25 00:24:16', 'videosonline/October2024/vqM0KHCndDQNp1pQarxB.jpg', '#7e0c6e', 'videosonline/October2024/BYGSjSRZXcQMvUTt2JyK.jpg', 'Photographie et Peinture, II', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Aaron Scharf, Art and Photography, The Pingouin Press, 1968\r\n\r\nJoël Petitjean, Gustave Courbet et la photographie, Fage éd., 2012\r\n\r\nThe Artist and The Camera : Degas to Picasso,  Catalogue d\'exposition, Dallas Museum of Art, 2000', '<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Albert Maignan, Hommage &agrave; Clovis II, 1883, huile sur toile, 109x1400cm, Mus&eacute;e de Beaux-Arts de Rouen, Rouen &nbsp; 2:37(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Francis Jourdain, L&rsquo;Art officiel de Jules Gr&eacute;vy &agrave; Albert Lebrun, 1949&nbsp; &nbsp; 2:25(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jan Van Beers, When Stars Set, av.1900, peinture, 94x135cm, Lukas State of the Art, Gent, Belgique &nbsp; 7:19(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jan Van Beers, Alice Antoinette de la Mar &agrave; cinq ans,&nbsp; c.1900, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; 7:47(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Mortimer Menpes, Umbrellas and Commerce, c.1887, gravure, Victoria and Albert Museum, Londres 8:29(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Cl&eacute;singer, Femme piqu&eacute;e par un serpent, 1847, statue en marbre, 56,5x180x70cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris&nbsp; 9:05(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Camille-F&eacute;lix Bellanger, Une Fin &agrave; l&rsquo;&eacute;cole pratique, 1902, lithographie,&nbsp; 53x75cm, dans The Cleveland Medical Library, Dittrick Museum of Medical History, Cleveland, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 11:09(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Albert Aublet, Arabic Madonna and Child (Vierge arabe et enfant), 1898, huile sur toile,&nbsp; Diocesan Museum in Płock, Plock, Pologne &nbsp; 12:04(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&laquo; Le Mars de Borgh&egrave;se et l&rsquo;instructeur Rodolphe &raquo;, d&eacute;tail, dans Surier Albert (dir.), La Culture physique, f&eacute;vrier 1904, Paris, p. 234, Biblioth&egrave;que Nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 13:40(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Buland, Nu masculin, 1875, huile sur toile, 81x65cm, &Eacute;cole nationale sup&eacute;rieure des beaux-arts, Paris &nbsp; 12:55(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Buland, Propagande, 1889, huile sur toile, 181,8x191,4cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; 14:20(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Buland, D&eacute;jeuner des laveuses, 1889, huile sur toile, 188x144,7cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:26(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Buland, Le Lendemain de la nuit de noces, 1884, huile sur toile, 150,3x113cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:55(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edmond Georges Grandjean, Le Boulevard des Italiens, 1889, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; 17:35(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Boulevard des Italiens, ca. 1890, carte postale, lieu inconnu &nbsp; 17:45(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">William Logsdail, St Martin-in-the-Fields, 1888, huile sur toile, 143,5x118,1cm, Tate Britain, Londres, Royaume-Uni &nbsp; &nbsp; 18:00(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">William Logsdail, Bank and the Royal Exchange, 1887, lithographie, crayon et plume, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 18:37(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, The Royal Exchange, c.1900, photographie, lieu inconnu&nbsp; 18:45(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Pascal Dagnan-Bouveret, Une S&eacute;ance chez le photographe, 1879, Mus&eacute;e de Beaux-Arts de Lyon, Lyon&nbsp; &nbsp; 18:59(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Lawrence Alma-Tadema, Sortie d&rsquo;&eacute;glise au XV&egrave;me si&egrave;cle,1864, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 19:43(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Lawrence Alma-Tadema, Preparations for the Festivities, 1866, huile sur toile, 54x69,2cm, Clark Arts Institute, Massachusetts, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 20:38(1)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text