>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Ernest Meissonnier, Campagne de France, 1814, 1864, huile sur bois, 51,5x76,5cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 9:36(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eadweard Muybridge, &laquo; Cheval au pas. 106 m&egrave;tres &agrave; la minute &raquo;, dans La Nature : revue des sciences, no. 289,&nbsp; premier semestre 1879, Ed. G. Masson, Paris, p. 24, Biblioth&egrave;que num&eacute;rique en histoire des sciences et des techniques, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 8:57(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eadweard Muybridge, &laquo; Petit galop. 1142 m&egrave;tres &agrave; la minute &raquo;, reproduction par l&rsquo;h&eacute;liogravure de photographies instantan&eacute;es, dans La Nature : revue des sciences, no. 289, premier semestre 1879, Ed. G. Masson, Paris, p. 24, Biblioth&egrave;que num&eacute;rique en histoire des sciences et des techniques, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 10:10(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eadweard Muybridge, &laquo; Galop. 200 m&egrave;tres &agrave; la minute &raquo;, reproduction par l&rsquo;h&eacute;liogravure de photographies instantan&eacute;es, dans La Nature : revue des sciences, no. 289, premier semestre 1879, Ed. G. Masson, Paris, p. 25, Biblioth&egrave;que num&eacute;rique en histoire des sciences et des techniques, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 10:10(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span>​</p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;douard Detaille, Charge de cavalerie : Vive l\'Empereur!, 1891, huile sur toile, 370x437,5cm, Art Gallery of New South Wales, Sidney, Australie&nbsp; &nbsp; 12:25(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Stanley Berkeley, Waterloo: Gordons and Greys to the Front, 18th June, 1815, 1898, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 12:35(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eadweard Muybridge, &ldquo;&ldquo;Annie G.&rdquo; Galloping&rdquo;, 1887, collotype, 21x32,9cm, Animal Locomotion: Animal Locomotion: An Electro Photographic Investigation of Consecutive Phases of Animal Movements, planche 627, vol. IX, 1887, Philadelphia Museum of Art, Philadelphia, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; &nbsp; 12:41(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Aim&eacute; Morot, La Bataille de Reichshoffen, 6 ao&ucirc;t 1870, 1889,&nbsp; huile sur toile, 430x800cm, Mus&eacute;e national du Ch&acirc;teau de Versailles, Versailles&nbsp; &nbsp; 12:52(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas, Pas battu, 1879, pastel sur monotype sur papier, Museum of Modern Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 13:18(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eadweard Muybridge, &ldquo;&ldquo;Annie G.&rdquo; Cantering. Saddled&rdquo;, 1887, collotype, 18,1x40,6cm, Animal Locomotion: Animal Locomotion: An Electro Photographic Investigation of Consecutive Phases of Animal Movements, planche 621, vol. IX, 1887, Philadelphia Museum of Art, Philadelphia, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 13:49(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas, Annie G. in canter (Annie G. au petit galop), c.1887, ND&nbsp; &nbsp; 14:02(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas, Racehorse with jockey (Jockey vu de profil), c.1887, sanguine sur papier, 28,3x41,8cm, Museum Boymans-van Beuningen, Rotterdam, Pays Bas &nbsp; 14:08(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eadweard Muybridge, &ldquo;Annie G.\" Walking, Saddled&rdquo;, 1887, detail, collotype, 18,9x40,3cm, Animal Locomotion: Animal Locomotion: An Electro Photographic Investigation of Consecutive Phases of Animal Movements, planche 580, vol. IX, 1887, Philadelphia Museum of Art, Philadelphia, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 14:14(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas,&nbsp; The Jockey (Jockey de profil), c.1889, pastel, fusain et crayon sur papier, 32,4x49,8cm, Philadelphia Museum of Art, Philadelphia, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 14:23(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Edgar Degas, Cheval au galop sur le pied droit, c.1890, sculpture, bronze &agrave; patine brun fonc&eacute;, 31x26x21cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; &nbsp; 15:46(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Thomas Eakins, A May Morning in the Park (The Fairman Rogers Four-in-Hand), 1879-1880, huile sur toile, 60,3x91,4cm, Philadelphia Museum of Art, Philadelphia, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; &nbsp; 16:25(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eadweard Muybridge, &laquo; Horses. Trotting&raquo;, photographie &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine, de la serie Abe Edgington Series, c.1878, dans The attitudes of animals in motion: a series of photographs illustrating the consecutive positions assumed by animals in performing various movements, executed at Palo Alto, California, in 1878 and 1879, no. 28, Library of Congress, Washington, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 16:53(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Family Tandem Bicycle, c.1910, photographie, ND&nbsp; &nbsp; 17:31(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Thure de Thulstrup, Wheeling on Riverside Drive, 1886, gravure sur bois sur papier blanc, 39x54cm, 17 juillet 1886, ND &nbsp; &nbsp; 18:29(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Arthur Berdett Frost, Tourists, Harper&rsquo;s Weekly, avril 1896&nbsp; &nbsp; 18:43(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Marcel Jacquier, Aumon Nantes, Pneus Dunlop, c.1920, affiche, 80x120cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 19:02(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;tienne-Jules Marey, Le Fusil photographique, 1882, Archives de la Cin&eacute;mat&egrave;que Fran&ccedil;aise, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;19:29(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;tienne-Jules Marey, &laquo; Mode d&rsquo;emploi de fusil photographique &raquo;, dans La Nature : revue des sciences,&nbsp; premier semestre 1882, Ed. G. Masson, Paris, p. 328, Biblioth&egrave;que num&eacute;rique en histoire des sciences et des techniques, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 19:49(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;tienne-Jules Marey, Homme qui marche, chronophotographie, 1883&nbsp; &nbsp; 20:03(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eadweard Muybridge, &ldquo;Homme nu marchant &raquo;, dans Animal Locomotion: Animal Locomotion: An Electro Photographic Investigation of Consecutive Phases of Animal Movements, planche 1, 1893, Philadelphia Museum of Art, Philadelphia, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 20:03(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;tienne-Jules Marey, Le Coup de marteau, c.1895&nbsp; 20:37(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">William Bell Scott, Iron and Coal: the Industry of Tyme, 1857-1861, aquarelle, 24,5x23,8cm, Victoria and Albert Museum, Londres, Royaume-Uni&nbsp; &nbsp; 20:16(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&Eacute;tienne-Jules Marey, Saut &agrave; la perche, 1888-1890,&nbsp; ND&nbsp; 22:33(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat, Le Chahut, 1889-1890, Kr&ouml;ller-M&uuml;ller Museum, Otterlo&nbsp; &nbsp; 20:49(2), 21:44(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat, Le Cirque, 1890-1891, huile sur toile, 186x152cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 24:00(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Rodin, Saint Jean-Baptiste, 1880, sculpture, bronze, 201x71,7x119,5cm, Mus&eacute;e Rodin, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 24:59(2)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">L&eacute;on Riesener, Portrait d&rsquo;Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix les mains lev&eacute;es, 1842, daguerr&eacute;otype, Petit Palais, Mus&eacute;e des Beaux-Arts de la Ville de Paris, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 1:00(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">L&eacute;on Riesener, Portrait d&rsquo;Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix de face, en buste, 1842, daguerr&eacute;otype, 6x4,3cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1:07(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Nadar, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix assis de trois-quarts face, la main dans le gilet, c.1857, impression &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine, 23x16,3cm, The Museum of Modern Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 1:14(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Etienne Carjat, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, 1857-1865, &eacute;preuve sur papier albumin&eacute; contrecoll&eacute;e sur carton, 9,5x6cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; 1:19(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Marcantonio Raimondi, Adam et &Egrave;ve sous l\'arbre de l\'arbre de la science du bien et du mal, estampe, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Raphael, 24x17,7cm, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 3:25(3), 4:25(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, [Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par [sic] Delacroix], 1854, planche XVI, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 4:25(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span>​</p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix,&nbsp; Autoportrait au fusain d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s daguerr&eacute;otype, ND &nbsp; 5:17(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Louis Camille d&acute;Olivier, Nu f&eacute;minin, 1855, papier sal&eacute;, 21x16cm, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 5:34(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, &Eacute;tude de femme nue de profil &agrave; gauche, mine de plomb &nbsp; 5:34(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Seated and Standing Male Nudes, 1855, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Durieu, mine de plomb, 23x27cm, Metropolitain Museum of Art, New York, Etats-Unis &nbsp; 6:18(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix, 1854, planche XV, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 5:21(3), 7:08(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix, 1854, planche III, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 5:21(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Homme nu assis de face, les jambes &eacute;cart&eacute;es, sur une peau de panth&egrave;re, 1854, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Durieu (planche XV), papier sal&eacute; d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s n&eacute;gatif papier,&nbsp; 17,8x12,8cm, Mus&eacute;e Bonnat-Helleu, Bayonne &nbsp; &nbsp; 5:37(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix,, 1854, planche V, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 5:41(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix, 1854, planche XIX, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 7:50(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par Delacroix, 1854, planche XX, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 7:50(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, &Eacute;tude d&rsquo;homme nu, 1854, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s Durieu, Mus&eacute;e Bonnat-Helleu, Bayonne &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eugène Delacroix, Trois &eacute;tudes d\'hommes, mine de plomb, 19,2x25,3cm, Musée des Beaux-Arts et d\'Archéologie de Besançon, &nbsp;Besançon &nbsp; 7:03(3), 7:41(3)?</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Homme nu debout de dos, tenant un bâton vertical, papier albuminé, 9,9x5,8cm, Collection Gérard Lévy, Musée du Louvre, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 6:58(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Homme nu assis sur une chaise, papier albuminé. 9,7x5,8cm, Collection Gérard Lévy, Musée du Louvre, Paris</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eugène Delacroix, &Eacute;tude de jambes d\'homme assis et &Eacute;tude d\'une tête, mine de plomb. 20,3x15,2cm, Musée des Beaux-Arts et d\'Archéologie de Besançon, &nbsp;Besançon &nbsp; 7:11(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, &laquo; Nu féminin assis sur un divan, la tête soutenue par un bras &raquo;, papier salé verni d\'après négatif papier, dans Eug&egrave;ne Durieu, Eug&egrave;ne Delacroix, [Photographies d\'apr&egrave;s des mod&egrave;les pos&eacute;s par [sic] Delacroix], 1854, planche XXIX, 14X9,5CM, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; 7:59(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Eugène Delacroix, Odalisque, 1857, huile sur bois, 39,5x31 cm, collection particulière&nbsp; &nbsp; 7:58(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Auguste Bonheur, Du b&eacute;tail par un lac, 1862, huile sur toile, 100,9x140,3cm, Dahesh Museum of Art, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; &nbsp; 11:36(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Victor Laisne, Portrait de Courbet &agrave; 34 ans, 1853, &eacute;preuve sur papier sal&eacute;, d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s un n&eacute;gatif papier, 23,2x16,5cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:16(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Courbet &agrave; Sainte-P&eacute;lagie, 1871-1872, huile sur toile, 92x72cm, Mus&eacute;e Courbet, Ornans&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:29(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Adolphe Braun, Le Ch&acirc;teau de Chillon, 1867, photographie, Mus&eacute;e de l&rsquo;&Eacute;lys&eacute;e, Lausanne &nbsp; 16:44(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Le Ch&acirc;teau de Chillon, 1874-1877, huile sur toile, 73x92cm, &nbsp; &nbsp; 17:14(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Julien Vallou de Villeneuve, &Eacute;tudes d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s nature, nu, no. 1930, avant 1854, photographie, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; 17:59(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, L\'Atelier du peintre. All&eacute;gorie r&eacute;elle d&eacute;terminant une phase de sept ann&eacute;es de ma vie artistique et morale, 1854-1855, d&eacute;tail, huile sur toile, 361x598cm, Mus&eacute;e d\'Orsay, Paris&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 18:07(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Julien Vallou de Villeneuve, &Eacute;tudes d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s nature, nu f&eacute;minin, no. 1940, 1853, papier sal&eacute; d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s n&eacute;gatif sur papier, invers&eacute;e, 12,2x16,4cm, Biblioth&egrave;que nationale de France, Paris &nbsp; &nbsp; 18:18(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Femme au perroquet, 1866, huile sur toile, 129,5x195,6cm, Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, Etats-Unis &nbsp; &nbsp; 18:29(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Courbet, Les Baigneuses, 1853, huile sur toile, 227x193cm, Mus&eacute;e Fabre, Montpellier&nbsp; &nbsp; 19:26(3), 20:59(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Corr&egrave;ge, Noli me tangere, c.1525, huile sur panneau sur toile, Museo del Prado, Madrid, Espagne&nbsp; &nbsp; 19:58(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Le Caravage, Le Martyre de Saint Matthieu, 1599-1600, d&eacute;tail, huile sur toile, 323x343cm, Chapelle Contarelli, &Eacute;glise Saint-Louis-des-Fran&ccedil;ais, Rome, Italie&nbsp; &nbsp; 20:31(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Julien Vallou de Villeneuve, &Eacute;tudes d&rsquo;apr&egrave;s nature, nu f&eacute;minin, no. 1936, 1853, papier sal&eacute; d&rsquo;apr&eg