\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson,&nbsp; Claude Monet, 1886, dans William Fuller, Claude Monet and his paintings, New York, &Eacute;tats-Unis,1899 &nbsp; &nbsp; 5:40(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson,&nbsp; Portrait of Claude Monet, 1888-1890, photographie, Terra Museum of American Art, Chicago, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 5:48(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson, Woman by the water, c.1891,&nbsp; cyanotype, 19,5x24,1cm, Terra Museum of American Art, Chicago, Etats-Unis &nbsp; 5:56(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson,&nbsp; Gossips (Femme lavant &agrave; la rivi&egrave;re), 1891-1892, huile sur toile, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 5:54(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson,&nbsp; Girl sewing (La Layette), 1892, huile sur toile, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 6:11(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson, Woman picking fruit, c.1891, cyanotype, 24x15,9cm, Terra Museum of American Art, Chicago, Etats-Unis &nbsp; 6:25(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson,&nbsp; Gathering plums (Femmes r&eacute;coltant des fruits), 1891, huile sur toile, 55,9x45,7cm, Georgia Museum of Art, University of Georgia, Georgia , &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; 6:25(4), 6:47(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson, Woman standing by a tree, 1889-1891, cyanotype, 24,8x19,7cm, Terra Museum of American Art, Chicago, Etats-Unis &nbsp; 7:08(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson, Potatoe Harvest, huile sur toile, 55.9 x 45.7 cms,1891, ND &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;7:08(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson, Two in a Boat, c.1891, &eacute;preuve &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine, 9,5x12,7cm, Terra Museum of American Art, Chicago, Etats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7:38(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Theodore Robinson, Two in a Boat (Deux en b&acirc;teau), 1891, huile sur toile sur carton, 23,8x34,9cm, The Phillips Collection, Art Gallery, Washington,&nbsp; &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 7:38(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Achille Quinet, &Eacute;glise du Panth&eacute;on, c.1870, &eacute;preuve &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine, 24,3x19,3cm, ND &nbsp; 8:59(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet, Boulevard des Capucines, 1873-1874, huile sur toile, 80,33x60,33cm, The Nelson-Atkins Museum of Art, Kansas, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 8:32(4), 10:45(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Adolphe Braun, Pont des Arts, 1867,ND&nbsp; 10:25(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Achille Quinet, Vue de Paris, c.1860, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10:55(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">George Washington Wilson, HMS Cambridge &agrave; Hamoaze, vue st&eacute;r&eacute;oscopique, gauche, 1861, ND &nbsp; 11:14(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet, Ships riding on the Seine at Rouen (B&acirc;teaux sur la Seine &agrave; Rouen), 1872-1873, huile sur toile, 37,7x46cm, National Gallery of Art, Washington, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 11:27(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet, Cath&eacute;drale de Rouen, Le portail et la tour Saint-Romain, plein soleil, 1894, 100,1x65,9cm, National Gallery of Art, Washington, &Eacute;tats-Unis&nbsp; &nbsp; 11:53(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Cath&eacute;drale de Rouen en 1881, reproduite dans Guy Pessiot, Histoire de Rouen: 1850-1900 en 500 photographies avant l\'apparition de la carte postale, Editions PTC, 1981 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 12:38(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Claude Monet, La Cath&eacute;drale de Rouen. Le portail vu de face, 1892, huile sur toile, 107x74cm, Mus&eacute;e d&rsquo;Orsay, Paris &nbsp; 12:57(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Hippolyte Jouvin, Place des Victoires, 1860-1865, d&eacute;tail, photographie st&eacute;r&eacute;oscopique &agrave; l&rsquo;albumine, Europeana Collections, La haye, Pays Bas&nbsp; 13:37(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Caillebotte,&nbsp; Le Boulevard, vu d\'en haut, 1880, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 13:30(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Caillebotte,&nbsp; Un Refuge, Boulevard Haussmann, 1880, huile sur toile, 81x100cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 14:32(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Martial Caillebotte, Rond-point, vue du balcon du 9, rue Scribe, c.1891, photographie, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 14:30(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Anonyme, Martial et Gustave Caillebotte, photographie, ND&nbsp; &nbsp; 14:00(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Martial Caillebotte, Moi au balcon ou Martial Caillebotte rue Scribe, 1891, ND&nbsp; 14:49(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Caillebotte, &nbsp;L&rsquo;Homme au balcon, Maurice Brault, c.1880, huile sur toile, 116x97cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 14:42(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Martial Caillebotte, Sc&egrave;ne nautique, ND</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Caillebotte, R&eacute;gates &agrave; Argenteuil, 1893, huile sur toile, 65x89cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 15:38(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Martial Caillebotte, Maurice Minoret ramant, 1878, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; 15:52(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Caillebotte,&nbsp; Partie de bateau, dit Canotier au chapeau haut de forme, 1877-1878, huile sur toile, 90x117cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:49(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Caillebotte, Aviron de plaisanciers sur l\'Yerres, 1877, huile sur toile, 81x116cm, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 15:58(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Caillebotte, Dessin pour &laquo; Les avironneurs sur l\'Yerres &raquo;, 1877, crayon sur papier, 17x25cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; &nbsp; 16:06(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Martial Caillebotte, Gustave Caillebotte et Berg&egrave;re sur la Place du Carrousel, 1892, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 17:05(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustave Caillebotte, Rue de Paris, Temps de pluie, 1877, huile sur toile, 212,2x276,2cm, Art Institute of Chicago, Chicago, &Eacute;tats-Unis &nbsp; 16:50(4)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n