ui-rich-text__text\">Ch&egrave;ne, Longuet, &laquo; Transfiguration du Sacro Monte di Varallo (Vals&eacute;sie) &raquo;, d&eacute;tail, phototypie n&eacute;gatif X, dans Jean-Martin Charcot (dir.), Nouvelle iconographie de la Salp&ecirc;tri&egrave;re, tome III, Ed. Lecrosnier et Bab&eacute;, Paris, p.286 &nbsp; 5:27(3), 5:54(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Martin Charcot (dir.), Nouvelle iconographie de la Salp&ecirc;tri&egrave;re, tome I, Ed. Lecrosnier et Bab&eacute;, Paris, 1888, p.17&nbsp; 6:20(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Jean-Martin Charcot (dir.), Nouvelle iconographie de la Salp&ecirc;tri&egrave;re, tome I, Ed. Lecrosnier et Bab&eacute;, Paris, 1888, p.19 &nbsp; 6:20(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Georges Seurat, Seated nude : Study for a &laquo; Baignade &raquo; (Gar&ccedil;on nu assis : &Eacute;tude pour une Baignade), 1883, cont&eacute; crayon on paper, 31,7x24cm, National Gallery of Scotland, &Eacute;dinbourg, &Eacute;cosse &nbsp; 6:34(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Madeleine Lemaire, Oph&eacute;lie, 1880, gravure, collection particuli&egrave;re&nbsp; &nbsp; 7:03(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">No&eacute; Bordignon, Matelda, huile sur toile, 193x121,9cm, collection particuli&egrave;re &nbsp; 7:03(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Paul Richer, &laquo; Attaque d&eacute;moniaque &raquo;, planche V, dans Paul Richer, &Eacute;tudes cliniques sur l\'hyst&eacute;ro-&eacute;pilepsie ou grande hyst&eacute;rie, Ed. Delahaye et Lecrosnier, Paris, 1881, p. 316&nbsp; 6:56(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Ch&egrave;ne, Longuet, &laquo; Contracture hyst&eacute;rique &raquo;, planche XIII, phototypie, n&eacute;gatif, dans Jean-Martin Charcot (dir.), Nouvelle iconographie de la Salp&ecirc;tri&egrave;re, tome IV, Ed. Bab&eacute; et Cie, Paris, 1891, &nbsp;p.122 &nbsp; 7:21(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">Gustav Klimt, Judith II, 1909, huile sur toile, 84x42cm, Ca\' Pesaro, Galleria Internazionale d\'Arte Moderna, Venise, Italie &nbsp; 7:11(3)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\">\r\n<li c